name: Cats Squared
description:
Navigate a strange world where gravity is flipped and mirrored and where Two cats form a square.
I had planned to make 12 levels but ran out of time, so there are only 7.
I also ran out of time to add sound effects. 

The color palette used.

The lower half is darkened versions of the original palette colors.

Made for Mini Jam 127 : Cats^2
